import org.apache.spark.sql._
import org.apache.spark.sql.types._

// break this down into rows and columns

val lines = spark.sparkContext.textFile("/var/lib/data/tcpdump.txt")
val fields =  Array(
    StructField("timestamp", StringType, false),
    StructField("remote", StringType, false),
    StructField("len", IntegerType, false))

val metrics = lines
  .map(_.split(" "))
  .filter(_.size == 8)
  .map(attrs => Row(attrs(0) + "T" + attrs(1), attrs(5), attrs(7).toInt))

val df = spark.createDataFrame(metrics, StructType(fields))
df.createOrReplaceTempView("tcpdump")

import org.apache.spark.sql._
import org.apache.spark.sql.types._

// extract this further...

case class Metric(timestamp: String, ip: String, port: Int, len: Int)

val lines = spark.sparkContext.textFile("/var/lib/data/tcpdump.txt")
val metrics = lines
  .map(_.split(" "))
  .filter(_.size == 8)
  .map(attrs => {
        val timestamp = attrs(0) + "T" + attrs(1)
        val remote = attrs(5)
        val (ip, port) = remote.splitAt(remote.lastIndexOf("."))

        Metric(timestamp,
            ip.replaceAll("\\.", "-"),
            port.stripPrefix(".").stripSuffix(":").toInt,
            attrs(7).toInt)
     })

val df = spark.createDataFrame(metrics)
df.createOrReplaceTempView("tcpdump")

%spark

import org.apache.spark.sql._
import org.apache.spark.sql.types._
import com.snowplowanalytics.maxmind.iplookups.IpLookups

case class Metric(timestamp: String, ip: String, port: Int, city: String, country: String, location: String, len: Int)

val lines = spark.sparkContext.textFile("/var/lib/data/tcpdump.txt")
val metrics = lines
  .map(_.split(" "))
  .filter(_.size == 8)
  .map(attrs => {
        val timestamp = attrs(0) + "T" + attrs(1)
        val remote = attrs(5)
        val (ip, port) = remote.splitAt(remote.lastIndexOf("."))

        val ipl = IpLookups(geoFile = Some("/var/lib/geo/GeoLiteCity.dat"))
        
        val (city, country, loc) = ipl.performLookups(ip)._1 match {
            case Some(geo) => (geo.city, Option(geo.countryName), Option(geo.latitude + "," + geo.longitude))
            case _ => (None, None, None)
        }
        
        Metric(timestamp,
            ip.replaceAll("\\.", "-"),
            port.stripPrefix(".").stripSuffix(":").toInt,
            city.getOrElse(""),
            country.getOrElse(""),
            loc.getOrElse("0,0"),
            attrs(7).toInt)
     })

val df = spark.createDataFrame(metrics)
df.createOrReplaceTempView("tcpdump")
